title: Ali Attoui
text:
Ali Attoui (born January 21, 1942 in <a href="Annaba">Annaba</a>) is a retired <a href="Algeria">Algeria</a>n international <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Career.
Attoui spent the majority of his career with <a href="Hamra%20Annaba">Hamra Annaba</a>, with brief stints with <a href="AS%20B%C3%B4ne">AS Bône</a>, and <a href="JBAC%20B%C3%B4ne">JBAC Bône</a>. He also represented <a href="Algeria%20national%20football%20team">Algeria</a> at the <a href="1968%20African%20Cup%20of%20Nations">1968 African Cup of Nations</a>.
